{"tid":1536174,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[律師建議］向法庭申請要地鐵攞CCTV。 緊急 請廣傳！","createTime":"2019-09-03T14:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T16:47:19.000Z","uid":57573,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ec9b8fd43863f937e2847dd4ed0b81676d7e8f9c","tid":1536174,"uid":57573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"[律師建議］ 緊急 請廣傳！<br />\n<br />\n831太子站當日有份俾人打嘅市民，請盡快聯絡律師做民事訴訟(personal injuries)，[img][img]向法庭申請要地鐵攞CCTV。[/img][/img]<br />\n<br />\n一定要快，如果過咗期限，地鐵話自動洗咗啲CCTV，到時就真係冇人知道太子發生過咩事。<br />\n<br />\n究竟3 個紅色病人去左邊？到底有無人死亡？到底在封站24小時內，警察，或不知是否是香港警察的速龍 做了些什麼？香港人必須知道真相！<br />\n<br />\n律師電話： <br />\n1. 星火同盟 98190979<br />\n2. 民陣 6549 9452<br />\n3. 民權觀察 9463 2945<br />\n4. 伍展邦律師行 2608 1400<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69720944_2423594921060650_2937725993734897664_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_oc=AQmgsnzxTbyYu1wgeDshDW48N-ZipSIMUUjf1MSbvx25RTagsQBdhiP7ZZzrmEhLAPc&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=9cd861c0bbffb2c0a2e8db6c20f9136d&amp;oe=5E0EDD2D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F69720944_2423594921060650_2937725993734897664_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_oc%3DAQmgsnzxTbyYu1wgeDshDW48N-ZipSIMUUjf1MSbvx25RTagsQBdhiP7ZZzrmEhLAPc%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D9cd861c0bbffb2c0a2e8db6c20f9136d%26oe%3D5E0EDD2D&h=efeab92f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa89386fc6de998a1ed9b40fa483ae8e94d53170","tid":1536174,"uid":6197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:56:25.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"e0b91378b961512cbc66326926ef1afba08baf16","tid":1536174,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:57:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3854e6de30a8dfbdea4cdd98fc4397bbe2d95452","tid":1536174,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:58:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0026e7f887046881ad59c577741ce0cbd4e06e49","tid":1536174,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:47:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">蘋果</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}